author: RYAN ZUMMALLEN of Edmunds
title: Keep your car clean to reduce coronavirus risk
description: The coronavirus can spread quickly inside a contained space such as the interior of a vehicle
content: The spread of the novel coronavirus, and its associated COVID-19 disease, is made worse because it is highly contagious. Since vehicle interiors are essentially small contained spaces, it is important to take steps to reduce the risk of contracting the virus … [+4337 chars]
